      <talk_question mid="57"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Sorceress Cynthia${action:Talk}<BR>Ah...Right! It is said that a door leading to <FONT color=#a82424>Marian's Shrine</FONT> was constructed a long time ago in <FONT color=#a82424>Frost Wind Forest</FONT>. Don't tell me the door still exists...<BR>That guy could actually find that door?</html>]]></talk_question>
