      <talk_answer link_index="n012_sorceress_master_cynthia-accepting-acceptted" mid="60" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Alright.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="59"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Sorceress Cynthia$<BR>It leads to the lowest floor of <FONT color=#a82424>Marian's Shrine</FONT>. The path is narrow and old so it will not be easy to get out from there.<BR>Head to <FONT color=#a82424>Marian's Shrine</FONT> now, you should be able to capture him before he escapes.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
