   <talk_paragraph index="n165_cleric_jake-2" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n165_cleric_jake-2-a" mid="16" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>What…? H-How can it be… You?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="15"><![CDATA[<html>$Cleric Jake$<BR>(Coughs) Huff huff…<BR>It was a good fight… hah…ha…<BR>You… are now good enough to fulfill the duites of a Templar Knight… Arrgh…</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n165_cleric_jake-2-a" image="QN_DragonSycophant.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n165_cleric_jake-2-b" mid="18" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Why... are you wearing a Dragon Follower's Mask? Why...?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="17"><![CDATA[<html>$Cleric Jake$<BR>Is it weird to see that… That I'm a <FONT color=#a82424>Dragon Follower</FONT>? Hah...<BR>(Coughs)</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n165_cleric_jake-2-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n165_cleric_jake-2-c" mid="20" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>... You... deceived us? Did you betray us?!</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="19"><![CDATA[<html>$Cleric Jake$<BR>... My mission... was to steal the <FONT color=#a82424>Sage's Staff</FONT> and <FONT color=#a82424>Vision Orb</FONT> from <FONT color=#a82424>Mana Ridge</FONT>…Though it took a little too long... Ha... (Coughs)</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n165_cleric_jake-2-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n165_cleric_jake-2-d" mid="22" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Why... Why did you turn to the dark side? Why?!</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="21"><![CDATA[<html>$Cleric Jake$<BR>I'm sorry.. But... I have no regrets, and I don't blame anyone...<BR>I was just doing what I had to do... You and I are on different paths... That's... That's all...</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n165_cleric_jake-2-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n165_cleric_jake-2-e" mid="24" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Nonsense! Enough with your excuses!</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="23"><![CDATA[<html>$Cleric Jake$<BR>(Coughs)<FONT color=#a82424>Good</FONT> and <FONT color=#a82424>Evil</FONT> are... just like <FONT color=#a82424>two sides of a coin</FONT>... (Coughs)... Which side appears will be decided by the circumstances... (Coughs)... Perhaps one day... your dark side will awaken as well...</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n165_cleric_jake-2-e" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n165_cleric_jake-2-f" mid="26" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Live and repent! If you die just like that... I.. I will wipe out all Dragon Followers!</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="25"><![CDATA[<html>$Cleric Jake$<BR>Ugghh… There's not much time left... I couldn't fulfill my dreams, but… I hope you can achieve yours. You will be enlightened when you break free from the norms... Live a life where... you are not controlled or forced by anyone...</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n165_cleric_jake-2-f" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n165_cleric_jake-3" mid="28" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>N-no! Open your eyes!</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="27"><![CDATA[<html>$Cleric Jake${action:Talk}<BR>Ha... Ha... This ain't... too bad...<BR><FONT color=#387206>{user_nick}</FONT>... My <FONT color=#a82424>brother</FONT>... We may not be related by blood... But I treated you as one of my own... The <FONT color=#a82424>ordeal</FONT>... is <FONT color=#a82424>yet to be over</FONT>. (Coughs)... I hope... you can achieve your goals...</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n165_cleric_jake-3" image="QN_Jake_Down.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="29"><![CDATA[<html>$Cleric Jake$<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Jake smiles faintly. You hold his still body close and shout his name but he does not respond... </FONT><BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>Your mind is in a chaotic mess with the pain from the betrayal of a trusted friend.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n013_cleric_tomas-3" image="QN_DragonSycophant.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n013_cleric_tomas-3-a" mid="31" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>I got the orb and the staff back…</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="30"><![CDATA[<html>$Cleric Thomas$<BR>Why... do you look so gloomy? Did you lose the <FONT color=#a82424>Dragon Follower</FONT>? W-where's the Orb and Staff...?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n013_cleric_tomas-3-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n013_cleric_tomas-3-b" mid="33" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Talk about Jake)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="32"><![CDATA[<html>$Cleric Thomas${action:Talk}<BR>You found them? Hahaha~ Great job!<BR>Thanks to you, the reputation of us <FONT color=#a82424>Templar Knights</FONT> will only get better!<BR>But… did something happen?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n013_cleric_tomas-3-b" image="QN_Jake_Down.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n013_cleric_tomas-3-c" mid="35" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>You once told me not to trust others so easily… You were worried about the pain I might get…</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="34"><![CDATA[<html>$Cleric Thomas${action:Talk2}<BR>W-what do you mean...?<FONT color=#a82424> Jake</FONT> was a <FONT color=#a82424>Dragon Follower</FONT>...?<BR><FONT color=#a82424>Jake</FONT> who fought against the evil more than anyone…? It can't be true…</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n013_cleric_tomas-3-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n013_cleric_tomas-3-d" mid="37" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>What was the dream he tried to achieve…?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="36"><![CDATA[<html>$Cleric Thomas$<BR>Jake... Argh...<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Thomas looks somber and remains quiet for a while)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n013_cleric_tomas-3-d" image="QN_Jake_Down.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n013_cleric_tomas-3-e" mid="39" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Jake... What was the dream that you believed in…? For what…?)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="38"><![CDATA[<html>$Cleric Thomas$<BR>I don't know what <FONT color=#a82424>Jake</FONT>'s goals were...<BR>But maybe he subconciously wanted to be stopped by you...<BR>I don't know what to say.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
